We are so proud to announce an Earth Month collab with the awesome team at @surfriderfiu apart of the respected @surfrider Foundation! 🌊

Find your purpose, peace, and new friends by coming together to clean one of Florida’s most beautiful beaches! 

Removing debris helps reduce the chances of innocent animals ( including dogs! ) from ingesting or getting caught up in these toxic materials! In addition, fish often mistakenly eat pieces of colourful plastic, which is passed along the food chain and eventually into us! 🐟🎣

@surfrider ‘s values align so well with Canine Crew and our members! Let’s pull together in celebration of Earth Month and inject some love into the world! 💕🌎🌲

If you need help with transport DM our page:)

Show up with a hat, suncream, sunglasses, and lots of water:) 

Rsvp in the bio:)
